			<div class="content" id="post-content-2056111">
									

<blockquote>
<p>I also really wish there was more content to these, and that they all weren't essentially the same poster with minor changes.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Fair enough on your assessment of the artwork; as I've said elsewhere the poster format makes it really hard to come up with images, and they DO need images. What I don't get it is that you seem to be disappointed that we're following a format. Yes, they're the same poster (and I disagree about minor changes, you're confusing the limitations on the amount of characters with a limit on creativity), but that's the point of a format: you take the base and fill in the blanks. If you measure SCP articles by the same standard, all of them are the same article with the words changed.</p>

							</div>

								
					
